## üì¶ Prerequisites

Before starting, ensure you have the following installed

### Required Software
- Node.js (v18.0.0 or higher) - [Download](httpsnodejs.org)
- PHP (v7.4 or higher) - Included in XAMPP
- MySQL (v8.0 or higher) - Included in XAMPP
- XAMPP (Apache + MySQL + PHP) - [Download](httpswww.apachefriends.org)
- Git - [Download](httpsgit-scm.com)
- Arduino IDE (for IoT device) - [Download](httpswww.arduino.ccensoftware)

### Hardware Requirements (for IoT)
- ESP8266 Development Board (NodeMCU or similar)
- DHT11 Temperature & Humidity Sensor
- Soil Moisture Sensor (Analog)
- Jumper Wires
- USB Cable (for ESP8266)

